rows.label: tlk70000026_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Since ancient times, Iira has always
had the blessing of the Divine Beast
and lived in peace and prosperity.

rows.label: tlk70000026_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Whatever happened, we've always
been able to overcome it with the
Divine Beast by our side, right?

rows.label: tlk70000026_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, this isn't official, but rumor has
it we're building a powerful cutting-edge
warship - and it's nearly done.

rows.label: tlk70000026_05_msg0004
rows.name:
So I think this time too we'll be
fine, as long as we stick together.
